{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Tile store enabled for accessing local tile packs and for loading new tile packs from server."}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode\/readAndUpdate"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStore-APIs","doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode"]]},"metadata":{"externalID":"c:@E@MBMTileStoreUsageMode@MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","roleHeading":"Case","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"readAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}],"symbolKind":"case","title":"TileStoreUsageMode.readAndUpdate"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"readAndUpdate","kind":"identifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"All tile requests are converted to tile pack requests, i.e.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the tile pack that includes the request tile will be loaded, and the tile extracted"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"from it. In this mode, no individual tile requests will be made.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This mode can be useful if the map trajectory is predefined and the user cannot pan"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"freely (e.g. navigation use cases), so that there is a good chance tile packs are already loaded"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in the vicinity of the user."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If users can pan freely, this mode is not recommended. Otherwise, panning"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"will download tile packs instead of using individual tiles. Note that this means that we could first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"download an individual tile, and then a tile pack that also includes this tile. The individual tile in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the disk cache won’t be used as long as the up-to-date tile pack exists in the cache.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://com.mapbox.MapboxMaps/documentation/Overview":{"type":"topic","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/Overview","kind":"article","title":"MapboxMaps Documentation","url":"\/documentation\/overview","abstract":[]},"doc://com.mapbox.MapboxMaps/documentation/MapboxMaps/TileStoreUsageMode/readAndUpdate":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/TileStoreUsageMode\/readAndUpdate","url":"\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/tilestoreusagemode\/readandupdate","title":"TileStoreUsageMode.readAndUpdate","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"case","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"readAndUpdate"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Tile store enabled for accessing local tile packs and for loading new tile packs from server.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MBMTileStoreUsageModeReadAndUpdate"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://com.mapbox.MapboxMaps/documenta